Method Detail

getPage

public <T> ResultSet<T> getPage(java.lang.String accessToken,
                                Pagination pagination,
                                java.lang.Class<T> objectClass)
                     throws ConstantContactServiceException
Generic method that returns a ResultSet of objects, based on a Pagination object and a specified object class.

Parameters:
accessToken - Constant Contact OAuth2 access token.
pagination - Pagination for fetching next set of data.
objectClass - The class of the objects that are expected in the ResultSet.
Returns:
A ResultSet of "objectClass" that containing data as returned by the server on success;
An exception is thrown otherwise.
Throws:
ConstantContactServiceException - When something went wrong in the Constant Contact flow or an error is returned from server.
